text:
Went to see Ildris.  Met a union leader goblin, she was not what I expected!  Really nice.  Malgrin and Ophira argued about that burning man, and what he said.  Ildris is pretty sure that was Bernard.  {d:Anima miser'da...:Poor unfortunate soul...}

Then Ophira complained about Malgrin AGAIN!  Why can't these two GET ALONG??!!? No {d:pactum:contract} seems to work with them!

Talked with Ophira for a long time.  She told me about her grandfather, and about her childhood.   Seems like she had it good... too good though, maybe.  I feel really bad for her.  But also kind of jealous.  She knew her family, but she lost them all.

I think I got through to her about Malgrin, though, eventually. She said she'll try, at least!

.... {d:Quid'inferi?!:What the fuck?!}
